---
source: crates/lt-tui/src/keymap/mod.rs
expression: "lines.join(\"\\n\")"
---
global   j / down                 -> move down
global   k / up                   -> move up
global   g g                      -> go to top
global   G                        -> go to bottom
global   ctrl+d                   -> half page down
global   ctrl+u                   -> half page up
global   pgdn                     -> page down
global   pgup                     -> page up
list     enter / space            -> open detail pane
list     /                        -> search
list     ctrl+/ / ctrl+7          -> open keyboard shortcuts
list     c                        -> create issue
list     s                        -> set status
list     p                        -> set priority
list     a                        -> set assignee
list     ctrl+r                   -> refresh
list     d                        -> toggle sort direction
list     o b                      -> open in browser
list     ctrl+n                   -> next page
list     ctrl+p                   -> previous page
list     L                        -> log in / re-authenticate
detail   c                        -> comment on issue
detail   o b                      -> open in browser
popup    enter                    -> confirm
new issue ctrl+enter / alt+enter   -> submit
new issue tab                      -> next field
new issue shift+tab                -> previous field
new issue enter                    -> confirm
new issue m                        -> assign to me
comment  ctrl+enter / alt+enter   -> submit
comment  esc                      -> cancel
search   enter                    -> confirm
search   ctrl+c                   -> clear query
search   down                     -> move down
search   up                       -> move up
search   ctrl+n                   -> next completion
search   ctrl+p                   -> previous completion
search   ctrl+y                   -> accept completion
search   tab                      -> complete forward
search   shift+tab                -> complete backward
help     down / j                 -> move down
help     up / k                   -> move up
overlay  esc / q                  -> close, back to the view beneath
list     esc                      -> refresh (press twice to reset sort/filter/search)
list     q                        -> quit
